text.tspan: The number of tests for each confirmed case
Figures are shown according to the number of days since the 5th confirmed death due to COVID-19 in that country.
Days since the total confirmed deaths of COVID-19 reached 5
Number of tests per confirmed case
Source: Official data collated by Our World in Data, European CDC – Situation Update Worldwide – Last updated 21st April, 11:45 (London time)
Note: There are substantial differences across countries in terms of the units, whether or not all labs are included, the extent to which negative
and pending tests are included and other aspects. Details for each country can be found at ourworldindata.org/covid-testing.
